BMW's Chief Executive Says Electric Cars Need State Aid to 2017, Welt Says

-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 
2011-03-02T03:01:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/bmw-s-chief-executive-says-electric-cars-need-state-aid-to-2017-welt-says.html
  Bayerische Motoren Werke AG  Chief
Executive Officer  Norbert Reithofer  said government aid will be
needed from 2012 to 2017 in order for sales of electric cars to
reach a “significant” volume, Welt said, citing an interview. 